{ Black attempts to hold his kingside together and prepares to meet hxg6 with ...hxg6.   5...h6?!  6.hxg6  fxg6  was seen in Pavalachandran-Wickramasinghe, Colombo 2020, where White went  7.Qd3  , but expansion in the centre would appear even stronger:  7.e4  Nb6  8.Nc3  Bg7  9.e5  . White blunts the bishop on g7 and simply prepares to target the rather vulnerable g6-pawn with Bd3 and also Nge2 and Nf4 if needed. }
