{ White dominates the centre and may simply complete development with Nf3, Bc4 @@StartBracket@@or Be2@@EndBracket@@ and Bg5, with the queen likely to head for d2 or b3.  The king can then be housed on either side, in contrast to which Black is likely to remain rather passive for some time, not least as he desperately tries to breathe life into both his bishops. }
